window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Another world needs a hero, and the greatest heroes are Magical Sword Knights. Just ask their swords.</p> <p>Squire Yorick and his Magical Sword Justice have been summoned to Kultai where a magical conjunction has gone off the rails. A Monster Army is threatening to wipe out the planet, and only a Magical Sword Knight can save them. Yorick must level up and learn new skills to confront this threat using the might of his magical sword. But is that all there is? Hidden on Kultai are the remnants of an ancient war and an ancient foe is rising back up to reclaim their lost power.</p> <p>Squire Yorick, his Magical Sword Justice, and his Mighty steed Gringer arrive on a new planet to team up with Izzy, a monster hunter, to defeat this threat.</p> <p><b>Book two in this new fact-paced, laugh-filled isekai LitRPG adventure from Ryan Rimmel, bestselling author of </b><b><i>Noobtown</i></b><b>.</b></p>"; 
